---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---
<PageLayout title="AI-Powered Basement Analytics | DrySpace Smart Monitor" description="Predictive flood risk, anomaly detection, and AI-powered maintenance recommendations. Your Smart Monitor learns your basement's patterns and warns you before problems happen.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-navy-900 text-white py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <a href="/smart-monitor" class="inline-flex items-center text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 mb-6 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
          </svg>
          Back to Smart Monitor
        </a>

        <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-cyan-500/10 border border-cyan-500/30 text-cyan-400 text-sm font-semibold mb-6">
          COMING 2027
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6">
          AI-Powered Analytics
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          Your Smart Monitor doesn't just report data — it learns. Predictive flood risk, pump failure detection, and maintenance recommendations powered by machine learning.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How AI Works -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">
          How AI Works
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
          Machine learning transforms raw sensor data into actionable intelligence
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Step 1: Collect -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-cyan-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">1. Collect</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Sensors feed thousands of data points daily. Water levels, pump cycles, humidity trends, weather data.
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Arrow connector (desktop only) -->
          <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-1/2 -right-4 transform -translate-y-1/2 z-10">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-cyan-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M13.025 1l-2.847 2.828 6.176 6.176h-16.354v3.992h16.354l-6.176 6.176 2.847 2.828 10.975-11z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2: Learn -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-cyan-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">2. Learn</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              ML models build a profile of YOUR basement. Normal patterns, seasonal cycles, response to weather events.
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Arrow connector (desktop only) -->
          <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-1/2 -right-4 transform -translate-y-1/2 z-10">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-cyan-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M13.025 1l-2.847 2.828 6.176 6.176h-16.354v3.992h16.354l-6.176 6.176 2.847 2.828 10.975-11z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3: Predict -->
        <div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-cyan-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">3. Predict</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Detect anomalies before they become emergencies. "Your pump will likely need replacement within 60 days."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AI Features -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">
          AI Features
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
          Advanced machine learning models tailored to basement monitoring
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Feature 1: Predictive Flood Risk -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Predictive Flood Risk</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Correlates sump level data with Environment Canada weather forecasts
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">24-hour flood probability score for your specific address</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">"High risk detected — heavy rain forecast + elevated water table"</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">Pre-storm alerts: "Verify sump pump before tomorrow's storm"</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">Accuracy improves with every season of data</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2: Pump Health Scoring -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Pump Health Scoring</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Tracks pump performance metrics over months
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">Runtime trending: gradual increase = impeller wear</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">Cycle frequency analysis: seasonal baselines</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">Pump Health Score: 0-100 (drops = service needed)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">"Your pump's efficiency has decreased 15% since October"</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 3: Mold Risk Engine -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Mold Risk Engine</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Combines humidity + temperature + duration
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">CDC/Health Canada mold growth models</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">"Conditions favorable for mold growth in next 48 hours"</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">Ventilation and dehumidifier recommendations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">Tracks cumulative exposure hours above thresholds</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 4: Radon Pattern Analysis -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 12l3-3 3 3 4-4M8 21l4-4 4 4M3 4h18M4 4h16v12a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V4z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Radon Pattern Analysis</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Seasonal radon cycle tracking (higher in winter)
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">Barometric pressure correlation (drops = radon spikes)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">Stack effect modeling for your home type</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">Long-term averaging vs. Health Canada 200 Bq/m³ guideline</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-3 text-slate-700">"Your 3-month average is 185 Bq/m³ — approaching action level"</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Smart Notifications -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">
          Smart Notifications
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
          AI-generated alerts that understand context and urgency
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-4">
        <!-- Notification 1: Storm Alert -->
        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 text-2xl">🌧️</div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-900 mb-1">Storm Alert</h3>
              <p class="text-blue-800 leading-relaxed">
                40mm rain forecast for Thursday. Your sump level is currently 8cm. Based on past storms, expect level to reach 22cm. Pump is healthy.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-blue-700 mt-2">2 days ago • Predictive Flood Risk</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Notification 2: Pump Anomaly -->
        <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 text-2xl">⚠️</div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-amber-900 mb-1">Pump Anomaly</h3>
              <p class="text-amber-800 leading-relaxed">
                Your pump ran 34 cycles today vs. 12-cycle daily average. No rain in forecast. Possible drain blockage or rising water table. Schedule inspection?
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-amber-700 mt-2">4 hours ago • Pump Health Scoring</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Notification 3: Mold Risk -->
        <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 text-2xl">🍄</div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-orange-900 mb-1">Mold Risk</h3>
              <p class="text-orange-800 leading-relaxed">
                Basement humidity has been above 58% for 72 hours. Current: 63%. Run dehumidifier or open windows to bring below 50%.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-orange-700 mt-2">1 day ago • Mold Risk Engine</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Notification 4: Maintenance Due -->
        <div class="bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-500 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 text-2xl">🔧</div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-900 mb-1">Maintenance Due</h3>
              <p class="text-purple-800 leading-relaxed">
                Your pump has logged 18,000 cycles since installation (Oct 2025). Average pump lifespan: 25,000 cycles. Schedule replacement within 6 months.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-purple-700 mt-2">1 week ago • Pump Health Scoring</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Insurance & Reporting -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-6">
              Insurance & Reporting
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              AI generates monthly "Basement Health Reports" that insurance companies accept as proof of continuous monitoring.
            </p>

            <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
